Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is even a faint scent
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that lingers from Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No way can we give up\Nafter coming this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see this through until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Until there's absolutely\Nno trace of Sasuke's scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Byakugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing... Please, find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no trace of Sasuke's scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done what we could...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the Hidden Leaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:35.95,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(746.25,576.25)}Battle of Unraikyo\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The preparations are already complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look upon the full moon,\Nit takes me back to that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the memories I've been trying to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can finally recall things\Nabout Itachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Faint memories buried deep in my heart\N are floating back to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Run...keep running...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and cling to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then one day, {\i1}come before me with\N{\i1}the same eye that I possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He was crying at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems what you told me was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to transplant Itachi's eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What Itachi wanted to see,\Nand what I will see hereafter, will be completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do as Itachi wished me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will restore the Uchiha clan\Nin my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... I need to talk to you,\NKisame Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,First Zetsu,\Nnow you come bothering me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually thought you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns out that you will be\Nthe last to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I had to deceive you,\Nthe person closest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would have guessed\Nthat Tobi was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm relieved...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're the one pulling the strings,\Nthat makes it easier for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Former Lord Mizukage...\NI mean, Madara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall continue to count on you, Kisame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Itachi is out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now, his little brother joins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What an interesting turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We, Taka, will destroy the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that, but how do you intend\Nto go about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to kill the Elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The others are not\Nour immediate concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you aim high,\Nthe ones below will shield them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You so-called "Taka" don't have\Nenough strength for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisame Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We still haven't settled that\Nlast game of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'm serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Suigetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke! You haven't trained them well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He stopped it with just his arm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu! Are you stupid?\NThis isn't the place to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My objective is his Shark Skin Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been hanging with Sasuke only\Nso I could get that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke... What'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it if you want to, Suigetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably can't beat him\Nyet anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...thanks a lot, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat you to some tasty shark's fin\Nsoon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Akatsuki is also low on manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to avoid unnecessary skirmishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph. Then you shouldn't\Ncriticize others, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We share common interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, Taka will work together\Nwith the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's in it for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give you a Tailed Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tailed Beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! It's like the Nine-Tails,\N with chakra physically manifesting as tails, they're mon-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They're chakra monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Originally, the First Hokage collected\Nseveral of them and kept them under his control.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Each time a Great Ninja War threatened,\N the Hokage Hashirama used them to maintain the power balance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and distributed them to other lands, starting with the\N five great nations, as proof of alliances or agreements.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You could call them\Nthe ultimate chakra weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a bad preposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if you betray the Akatsuki,\Nyou will die accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There are nine Tailed Beasts\Nin this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Akatsuki has collected six so far...\Nso there are three left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Akatsuki and Taka will split up\Nto hunt the remaining three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That is our immediate goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have the Nine-Tails yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Taka will capture the Eight-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Akatsuki will hunt the rest.\NWhich includes Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It went well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi is dead...\NSo our eyesore's finally gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, we need no longer keep our\N pact to stay away from the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We've waited so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All so we could proceed\Naccording to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But Itachi had placed insurance\Nin Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Amaterasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi believed that no one knew\Nthe truth about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So why go so far...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,True intentions aside,\N he probably feared I would try to recruit Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But...who would have thought that the Akatsuki\N would lose so many members to get to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We had problems at every turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone made a valuable contribution\Nin their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Deidara... Sasori... Hidan... Kakuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Without them,\Nwe could not have gotten this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to them, the scenario is\Nplaying out just as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Most importantly...\NI've won Sasuke over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Where is this thing called\N"the Eight-Tails"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take us lightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no intention\Nof telling you a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the Yotsuki clan,\Nnever betray our comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That is-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Doubt exists...in a fearful heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu, enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's under Sasuke's genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shucks... I was just getting\Nto the fun part.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where the Eight-Tails is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He is training...at Unraikyo,\NStorm Cloud Ravine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Any distinguishing features?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He...wields eight blades...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And has bull horns tattooed on his...\Nleft cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sheesh...\N{\i1}Those eyes of his have improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now he's even more difficult\N{\i1}to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh wow...\N{\i1}Sasuke's gotten even cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a nice place...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I could control\N{\i1}my impulses here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's calming...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You make my eyes hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Noon already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, bastard! Screw you, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Training from mornin',\Nstomach so starvin'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a rap-lovin' guy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and just decided on sukiyaki for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the Jinchuriki host\Nof the Eight-Tails?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's Lord Eight-Tails. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, "Are you Lord Jinchuriki?" Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to capture you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You have to say,\N"Please allow me to capture you, sir."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu, you take the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Jugo, you take the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin, get behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in the middle of our conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's some serious advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't kill the Jinchuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what the Akatsuki\Ntold us, Suigetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel his chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, talk about a showy diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who gets\Nto dig me is me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So scram, you fools, or I'll blast y'all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools... Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu, get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm peeking through...\NAnd see you alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But y'all are so brainless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My thirst for blood is my courage...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Making me so optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My blades are swirlin',\Nbut my store's a closin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Making for a blow-out sale\Nfor my performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got spare power and\Nmy appeal is glowing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight-Tails the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer Bee, that's me! Ah! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Start fighting and\Nyou're gonna be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cuz you'll be torn apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bit my tongue...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's totally crazy, but that Jugo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He keeps dodging\N{\i1}my Executioner's blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You made me bite my tongue... Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the heck are you all?\NFools... You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's getting on my nerves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?\NWhy would you capture me? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't owe you an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy who talks in weird verses...\Nis such a pain to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to obtain power\Nas quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's your prerogative...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I also want to confirm whether the Akatsuki's\N verbal promise is true or false and get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, we're the ones who\Nare going to use the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes without question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-You are so cool, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew he wouldn't let himself\N{\i1}be used as a pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's get to it and\Nsilence this irritating rapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to.
